flowchart TB
    U[User]
    FE[Web Frontend<br/>Chat + Voice + File]
    API[FastAPI Backend]
    AUTH[Auth + RBAC + Tenant Scope]
    ORCH[LLM Orchestrator]
    TOOLS[Tool Layer<br/>Inventory/Orders/Customers/Notifications]
    RULES[Rules Engine<br/>Threshold + Scheduled Jobs]
    NOTIFY[Notification Gateway<br/>WhatsApp/SMS/Email]
    DB[(PostgreSQL)]
    CACHE[(Redis)]
    FILES[(Object Storage)]
    AUDIT[(Audit Log Store)]
    ANALYTICS[Analytics Service]
    DASH[Dashboard API + UI Widgets]
    OBS[Monitoring + Alerting]
    BACKUP[Backup + Restore Pipeline]

    U --> FE
    FE --> API

    API --> AUTH
    API --> ORCH
    API --> DB
    API --> FILES
    API --> AUDIT
    API --> ANALYTICS

    ORCH --> TOOLS
    TOOLS --> DB
    TOOLS --> NOTIFY
    TOOLS --> FILES

    RULES --> CACHE
    RULES --> DB
    RULES --> NOTIFY
    RULES --> AUDIT
    API --> RULES

    ANALYTICS --> DB
    ANALYTICS --> AUDIT
    ANALYTICS --> DASH
    FE --> DASH

    API --> OBS
    RULES --> OBS
    NOTIFY --> OBS
    DB --> BACKUP
